---
title: Jerk Chicken Bowls with Rice, Beans and Pineapple Salsa
description: Feel the heat with jerk-spiced chicken! Hearty beans and rice form a delicious base, while a fresh pineapple salsa tops the chicken. If the kids don't like heat, toss their chicken in garlic salt. It's a win-win situation!
